Go to interaction button on top of the page and click on create new communication
--> Select Communication type
--> Select Interaction code Like General advising email or any option of your own
--> Select from address (Jenzabar allows you to access to mulitple users)
--> Select To (You will contacts in drop down box you can choose either people or dataset)
--> Select Contact type (like Institutional Priority)
--> Add "Subject" (like any description about the meeting)
--> Enter Body like main context of the meeting
Finally, click sent.
We can add note in Communication type tab also.
